* This is encoded in Apple's &quot;near DVD&quot; format.  It has been confirmed that these encodes work on all iPod devices capable of video playback (ty VoV).

* Regarding the filename prefix, if you use uTorrent to download, at the top it says Save As when you load the torrent, you can remove the prefix here.  It should still seed and download ok.

* This release was tested on Apple iPod 5g 30GB (MA002LL) v1.3.

* I am told this works fine on Zune devices also.

